

REQUIREMENTS :
--------------

    * Apache 2
    * PHP 5 >= 5.2.0
    * PHP-PGSQL or PHP-MYSQL
    * PHP-PCNTL
    * PHP-GETTEXT
    * PEAR SOAP class
    * PostgreSQL 8.x or MySQL 5.x
    * Use PHPAGI 2.14 included (http://phpagi.sourceforge.net written by Matthew Asham)
	* Freetype (for signup captcha)
	
	* Perl (CallBack Daemon)
		o Perl >= 5.6.1
		Perl module DBD::Pg
		Perl module DBD::MySQL
		Perl module Config::IniFiles
		
		yum install perl-DBD-MySQL perl-DBD-Pg perl-DBI
	
	* etc...
